<div id="pf3" class="pf w4 h15" data-page-no="3"><div class="pc pc3 w4 h15"><img class="bi x0 y0 w5 h16" alt="" src="bg3.png"/><div class="t m8e x57 h17 y71 ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Northern European Division Thanks God for You. </div><div class="t m8f x14 h18 y72 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In 1981, when Sabbath Schools </div><div class="t m90 x57 h18 y73 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worldwide last focused attention on Northern Europe, we told you of our plans for an </div><div class="t m91 x57 h18 y74 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evangelistic center in Poland, a school above the Arctic Circle in Norway, and a new building </div><div class="t m92 x57 h18 y75 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for Toivonlinnan Junior College in Finland. Of the $1,582,888.30 you gave that thirteenth </div><div class="t m93 x57 h18 y76 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath, 25 percent ($395,722.07) was shared among the three projects. Because of </div><div class="t m94 x57 h18 y77 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">difficulties in obtaining materials, the building in Poland was delayed, but construction has </div><div class="t m95 x57 h18 y78 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">begun on the college building in Finland, and the school building in north Norway (pictured </div><div class="t m96 x57 h18 y79 ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">above) is already in use. These children express the appreciation we all feel. </div><div class="t m97 x58 h18 y7a ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Special Projects portion of this quarter&apos;s offering on June 30 will be divided between </div><div class="t m98 x57 h18 y7b ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">library extension at Newbold College in England and the construction of an evangelistic center </div><div class="t m99 x57 h18 y7c ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in Eindhoven in the southern Netherlands. Thank you again for your prayers and generosity on </div><div class="t m9a x57 h18 y7d ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our behalf. </div><div class="t m9b x59 h18 y7e ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Walter R. L. Scragg, President, Northern European Division </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
